u_n = \dfrac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(\dfrac{i}{n}\right)^2\,\sin\left(\dfrac{i\,\pi}{n}\right)
\lim\limits_{n\rightarrow \infty}\dfrac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(\dfrac{i}{n}\right)^2\,\sin\left(\dfrac{i\,\pi}{n}\right) =  \dfrac{1}{\pi} - \dfrac{4}{\pi^3}
\sin\left(\dfrac{i \pi}{n}\right)
\sin \theta = \dfrac{1}{2i}(e^{i\theta}-e^{-i\theta})
\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty}\dfrac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(\dfrac{i}{n}\right)^2\,\sin\left(\dfrac{i\,\pi}{n}\right) = \int_0^1 dx \: x^2 \sin{\pi x}
